cdata.name: VeriME
cdata.desc:
VeriME is an online blockchain-based platform that works as an intermediary validation-as-a-Service (VaaS). Users can storeauthenticated personal data andallow its access to their service providers, that can validate the information already verified by VeriME. The platform main role isease the KYC(Know Your Customer) processes.

The VME, is an Ethereum-based token that serves as the underlying mean of value within the VeriME ecosystem.It can also be used to conduct KYC procedures via the platform.
